description:
I can’t believe 5 years of recording this glorious podcast has flown by! This podcast has inspired, healed and connected me in ways I can’t even describe and I know it has had the same impact on so many of you. It truly has been such a profound journey and in this episode, I wanted to share clips of the top 10 most downloaded episodes EVER on Highest Self Podcast. Can you guess what they are?! We’ll be starting with episode 10 and working our way to episode 1. I am also doing a GIVEAWAY of 10 Rose Gold Goddesses Memberships (value of $888) for those who leave a review + share their favorite episode on their IG story and tag me @iamsahararose! I am also giving EVERYONE who reviews the podcast my Discover Your Soul’s Purpose Meditation Course FREE! Just email me your review at pr@iamsahararose.com.

Tune into the 10 episodes:

393: Reclaiming Your Inner Witch, Sharing Your Voice + Healing The Feminine Wound with Mia Magik - https://iamsahararose.com/single-post/highest-self-podcas/
406: Ascension, Spirit Guides, Past Lives, Deities + Auras with Shaman Axel Carrasquillo - https://iamsahararose.com/single-post/highest-self-podcast-406-ascension-spirit-guides-past-lives-deities-auras-with-shaman-axel-carrasquillo/
402: How To Spiritually Protect Yourself Using Law of One with Krista Williams - https://iamsahararose.com/single-post/highest-self-podcast-402-how-to-spiritually-protect-yourself-using-law-of-one-with-krista-williams/
373: How To Raise Your Vibration + Create Your Own Reality with Aaron Doughty - https://iamsahararose.com/single-post/highest-self-podcast-373-how-to-raise-your-vibration-create-your-own-reality-with-aaron-daughty/
001: Who Is Your Highest Self? Intro to the Highest Self Podcast with Sahara Rose - https://iamsahararose.com/single-post/highest-self-podcast-episode-001-who-is-your-highest-self/
002: How I Became My Highest Self, Discovered My Dharma and Wrote The Idiot's Guide to Ayurveda with Sahara Rose - https://iamsahararose.com/single-post/highest-self-podcast-episode-002-how-i-became-my-highest-self-and-wrote-the-idiots-guide/
377: Choosing Intuition Over Fear with Mark Nepo - https://iamsahararose.com/single-post/highest-self-podcast-377-choosing-intuition-over-fear-with-mark-nepo/
382: Divine Feminine Truth, Embodiment + Body Sovereignty with Rev. Briana Lynn - https://iamsahararose.com/single-post/highest-self-podcast-382-divine-feminine-truth-embodiment-body-sovereignty-with-rev-briana-lynn/
381: Law of Attraction Techniques with the Secret Creator Rhonda Byrne - https://iamsahararose.com/single-post/highest-self-podcast-381-law-of-attraction-techniques-with-the-secret-creator-rhonda-byrne/
389: How To Manifest Anything (that is in alignment) with Cassandra Bodzak - https://iamsahararose.com/single-post/highest-self-podcast-389-how-to-manifesting-anything-that-is-in-alignment-with-cassandra-bodzak/
